{"tid":847363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登班窮撚真係好無知，唔講以為全香港既人都係供緊樓","createTime":"2018-10-04T06:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T04:46:46.000Z","uid":214534,"like":16,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"737615c072a6e560e80813855b23dd0429e5dcda","tid":847363,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T06:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/140357_daa4b751288efb21aefd1bedc5589e9e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F140357_daa4b751288efb21aefd1bedc5589e9e.png&h=4bc6a647&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/140359_44ad41a66251f33ffd58f6f5fa2d1b15.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F140359_44ad41a66251f33ffd58f6f5fa2d1b15.png&h=6c652192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時真係唔好怪人地笑你地無知窮撚階層<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上轉政府統計處睇下，香港既私樓入面有六成係供斷<br />\n即係得返四成係供緊，係你地口中既所講既樓爆會影響到既一群人<br />\n<br />\n而呢四成入面，我諗至少有一半都係四大長老幫拖，而無論咩情況下，四大長老都會奮身救佢既（係呀唔似得你地既窮父母，想幫你或者救你都冇能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n有時唔好話人笑鳩係地窮撚<br />\n窮撚唔知心胸狹窄，連思想智慧都狹窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bccb55439bebe3ef6204dee48a5f7db307b41f7","tid":847363,"uid":146535,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T06:14:34.000Z","msg":"供斷左嗰啲好多都冇錢買屬於自己嘅樓<br />\n簡單講屈住喺自己屋企<br />\n<br />\n當然佢地唔選供緊樓<br />\n係因為首期都冇"},{"pid":"b77b19276308fe35a3e04fbc16a65172ba18dc2c","tid":847363,"uid":181905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T06:29:42.000Z","msg":"幾時有私樓仔同公屋仔出黎互斬"},{"pid":"15dfdffb272653798a1a10c120b7454aacfd6438","tid":847363,"uid":214534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bccb55439bebe3ef620